title: ScrapItt

creator: Shopdibz Developers
descriptionHtml:
Welcome to ScrapItt - Where Story-Telling & Creativity Takes Center Stage! 🚀

Ditch the ordinary and step into a world of boundless possibilities. ScrapItt is not just another social media platform; it's a vibrant canvas for your imagination. We bring back the Orkut memories. 🎨💡

🌟 Unleash Your Creativity: Express yourself like never before with an array of cutting-edge tools and filters. Craft stunning visuals, share captivating scraps & moments, and let your creativity run wild.

💬 Connect & Collaborate: Make meaningful connections with like-minded individuals and ignite collaborations that spark brilliance. Our community thrives on support, inspiration, and genuine connections.

📈 Amplify Your Reach: Our powerful algorithms ensure your masterpieces reach the right audience at the right time. Watch your presence grow and your impact skyrocket.

🛡️ Toxic-Free Zone: Leave negativity at the door. ScrapItt is a safe haven where free speech is celebrated, and positivity reigns supreme. Embrace the spirit of camaraderie and encouragement.

🌐 Seamlessly Social: From direct scraps to sharing unforgettable moments, ScrapItt is your one-stop hub for all things social. Connect effortlessly and let your social life thrive.

📞 Personalised Number: The custom audio call feature of ScrapItt provides users with a unique and personalised phone number for seamless communication with friends.


Ready to embark on a journey of digital artistry and authentic connections? Join ScrapItt today and let your imagination soar!

🔥🔥🔥 Tap that "Sign Up" button and let the magic begin! 🎉
descriptionShort: Scrap it the new way!.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Change scrap privacy after posting.
Updated reshare UI.
Bug fixes & improvements.

Thank you! Enjoy ScrapItt.
